---
title: Teriyaki Sea Bass Rice Bowl with Mangetout and Kiwi Salsa
description: This Teriyaki Sea Bass Rice Bowl is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R41_W18_UK_HVP18925-4_Main_low-6a0b31e9.jpg
